channel.title: Monte Carlo
channel.desc: Romance 2011 Grace's vacation in Paris takes an unexpected twist when she's misidentified as a rich British heiress. With her best friend and stepsister, she embarks on an adventure to Monte Carlo, uncovering lives of privilege, royalty, and love along the way. Selena Gomez, Leighton Meester, Katie Cassidy, Cory Monteith, Andie MacDowell, Thomas Bezucha, April Blair.
